    "patch_code": "private void copyAttributes(org.jsoup.nodes.Node source, Element el) {\n     List <Attribute> attrList;\n    if (!source.attributes().isEmpty() ){\n         attrList =  new ArrayList<>(source.attributes().size());  \n       source.attributes().asList().forEach(attr -> {\n            \n      if(!(attr.getKey().matches(\"[-a-zA-Z0-9_:.]\"))){\n          return;\n          \n      }else {\n          \n          attrList.add(attr);\n      }});\n  \n       for (Attribute attribute : attrList) {\n               \n           \n            el.setAttribute(attribute.getKey(), attribute.getValue());\n        } \n    }\n else {\n       el.setAttribute(\"\",\"\");\n   }}",
